en.title: FusionExcel Welcomes 5 Former Miss Malaysia at Headquarter!
en.content: FE is proud to welcome 5 former Miss Malaysia at Headquarter recently. The 5 Miss Malaysias, Maggie Loo, Datuk Yasmin Yusuf, Nancie Foo, Samantha Shubert and Deborah Henry met with FE's Founder CEO Paul Ting to collaborate on FE's "Hope For Children" Charity project. As usual, no meeting is complete without a demonstrations of FE's amazing QP. FE's PD KC Phoon had the honour to perform the demostration with Deborah Henry (Miss Malaysia / World 2008). Everyone was very impressed by the power of FE's scalar energy QP!
